1. To create the dockerfile we need dependencies which will provide by the developers.

2. we need to write the dockerfile

3. we need to create the image from dockerfile.

4. docker build -t <image_name> .

5. run the container from the image using the commands.

6. docker run -d --name <container_name> -p 5000:5000 <image_name>

7. you can check from the browser.

8. whatever in the server.js file same data will appear when we browse in the browser.

